lead_paragraph: Despite being former midfield heroes for the clubs they now manage, Barcelona coach Luis Enrique and his Real Madrid counterpart Zinedine Zidane are afforded little credit for their achievements in management.

headline.print_headline: Zidane and Luis Enrique Get Little Credit Despite Feats
